skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: help me choose a pet
des: Sometimes you need to decide what pet you should get. Ask Alexa for advice before making a decision on a pet. Say "Alexa, help me choose a pet" to go through a series of questions and get pet advice based on your answers.
